    <title>Oceans contributor: Connie and Peter Roop</title>
    <description>Connie and Peter Roop are the authors over 100 children’s books about nature, science, and history. Former educators, the Roops now write and lecture fulltime and have given presentations on all seven continents. They are currently writing nature books for young readers for the American Museum of Natural History.
</description>
